               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of the Archangel Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡,  Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡, Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡, Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from = "1r" to = "19r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1860Malkea"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from = "21r" to = "41r"/><title type = "complete" ref="LIT4131Salam"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from = "41r" to = "62v"/><title type = "complete" ref="LIT4112Salam"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from = "63r" to = "71r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2965RepCh246"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    በሰላመ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ፡ በላዕለ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘአ፡ ዘአዕረፈ። ከመ፡ እዜኑ፡ ኅዳጠ፡ ወአኮ፡ ትሩፈ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>

